{"id":566646,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/08/【立此存照】江天勇案公开庭审中-编造出的telegram对话/","date":"2017-08-23T11:23:09Z","modified":"2017-08-24T03:12:56Z","title":"【立此存照】江天勇案公开庭审中 编造出的Telegram对话","content":"<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>【更正】经读者指出，由于编辑对司法电子取证的解读有误，本文列出的内容无法证明对话为检方编造的。</strong></span><strong>（</strong><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/08/%e3%80%90%e5%a3%b0%e6%98%8e%e3%80%91%e5%85%b3%e4%ba%8e%e6%b1%9f%e5%a4%a9%e5%8b%87%e6%a1%88%e5%ba%ad%e5%ae%a1telegram%e5%af%b9%e8%af%9d%e4%b8%80%e6%96%87/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">声明链接</a>）</strong></p>\n<p><del datetime=\"2017-08-24T02:55:40+00:00\"><strong>【编者注】</strong>近日，长沙中级人民法院在其官方微博发布了江天勇案公开审理的<a href=\"http://weibo.com/tv/v/FigcdBia1?fid=1034:2f9ddfa7e6b3b33c4cd9e0c0d4d97b70\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">视频</a>。在这场控辩双方煞有介事的照本宣读中，公诉人用来作为证据的一些 Telegram 截图很显然并不是来自该软件，更像是照着微信界面编造出的。</del></p>\n<p><del datetime=\"2017-08-24T02:55:40+00:00\"><strong>1. 创造性地将 Telegram 与QQ混搭。</strong>事实是，根本不存在“电报号”这种东西。Telegram 账户一般都绑定手机号，用户也可以创建用户名以便他人搜索——但谁会创建10位数字类似QQ号的用户名？</del></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_566650\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-566650\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"308\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案1.jpg 2394w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案1-300x176.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案1-768x451.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案1-1024x601.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案1-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@长沙中级人民法院 庭审视频截图</span></p></div>\n<p><del datetime=\"2017-08-24T02:55:40+00:00\"><strong>2. 照着微信界面编 Telegram 对话。</strong>法庭上呈现的更像是微信的聊天界面，对话框从形状到颜色都与 Telegram 完全不同。另外， Telegram 一对一对话不显示头像，群聊只显示头像和名字，信息发送成功后会显示绿色小勾（文末附官方版聊天界面截图）。下次编“对话”的时候别忘了。</del></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_566652\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-566652\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"302\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案3.jpg 2390w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案3-300x172.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案3-768x442.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案3-1024x589.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@长沙中级人民法院 庭审视频截图</span></p></div>\n<p>del datetime=&#8221;2017-08-24T02:55:40+00:00&#8243;&gt;<strong>3. 你见过一行能容下39个汉字的聊天软件么？</strong>&lt;如有的话也请读者联系我们，数字时代会作更正。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_566651\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-566651\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案2.jpg 2410w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案2-300x178.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案2-768x456.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案2-1024x608.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/谢阳案2-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">@长沙中级人民法院 庭审视频截图</span></p></div>\n<h4><strong>附：</strong></h4>\n<p><strong>江天勇律师的预言</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_566657\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/江天勇的预言.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-566657\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/江天勇的预言.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/江天勇的预言.jpg 2480w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/江天勇的预言-300x174.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/江天勇的预言-768x445.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/江天勇的预言-1024x593.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">除了最后一句，全部都成真了；庭审视频截图</span></p></div>\n<p><del datetime=\"2017-08-24T02:55:40+00:00\"><strong>Telegram 安卓版聊天界面</strong></del></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_566647\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/android.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-566647\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/android.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"494\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/android.png 547w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/android-182x300.png 182w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">图片来源：谷歌应用商店Telegram下载页</span></p></div>\n<p><del datetime=\"2017-08-24T02:55:40+00:00\"><strong>Telegram iOS版聊天界面</strong></del></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_566649\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/iphone.jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-566649\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/iphone.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/iphone.jpeg 392w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/08/iphone-169x300.jpeg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\